Annotation Type RangeKey

  • Deprecated. 
    use @SortKey instead

    @Inherited
 @Documented
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value={PARAMETER,ANNOTATION_TYPE})
public @interface RangeKey
    Annotates range key. This annotation is not required if the name of the argument contains word range or sort.
